<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Already submitted — <%= @prompt.tenant.dealership_name %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; max-width: 640px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; color: #222;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 22px;">Got it — submission received.</h1>
    <p>
      We have your <%= @prompt.request.metric_key.to_s.tr("_", " ") %>
      for <%= @prompt.scheduled_for.in_time_zone(@prompt.tenant.time_zone).strftime("%B %Y") %>.
      Thanks for the quick turnaround.
    </p>
    <p style="color: #555;">If you've come back to this link from a previous submission, this is the same screen — your data is already on file.</p>
    <p>Need to amend it? Reply to your most recent email from Rogue and we'll help.</p>
  </body>
</html>
